summary: An email from an Assistant U.S. Attorney in the Southern District of New York serving a grand jury subpoena to TD Ameritrade, dated August 12, 2019. This indicates an active criminal grand jury investigation was seeking financial records.

persons.name: Assistant U.S. Attorney
persons.context: The sender of the email serving a grand jury subpoena to TD Ameritrade in connection with a criminal investigation.

events.title: Grand Jury Subpoena Served to TD Ameritrade
events.description: A grand jury subpoena was served to the financial institution TD Ameritrade in connection with a criminal investigation.

keyFacts: A criminal grand jury investigation was active as of August 2019.
The investigation involved issuing subpoenas to financial institutions, specifically TD Ameritrade.
The subpoena was served by an Assistant U.S. Attorney from the Southern District of New York.
The document is an email correspondence regarding the service of legal process.
